# RCSB PDB Pipeline — Target Discovery Dataset Builder

Fetch, transform, and export RCSB PDB structural data for UniProt-identified proteins,
producing ML-ready datasets for drug target discovery.

```text
Input: UniProt IDs → [Search API] → PDB IDs → [Data API] → Raw data → [Transform] → Clean dataset
```

---

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install
pip install -e .

# Run full pipeline (minimal example)
rcsb-pipeline run --uniprots P01116,P04637 --output ./training_data

# Run with presets and all outputs
rcsb-pipeline run \
  --uniprot-file targets.txt \
  --preset standard \
  --granularity per-structure \
  --dedup-strategy keep-best \
  --missing-action fill-mean \
  --format csv \
  --format parquet \
  --output ./training_data
```

