## Installation

```bash
# From the rcsb_pipeline directory
pip install -e .

# Verify
rcsb-pipeline --help
```

### Dependencies

| Package | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `rcsb-api>=1.7.0` | Official RCSB Python client (Search + Data APIs) |
| `typer>=0.12.0` | CLI framework |
| `pydantic>=2.0` | Configuration validation |
| `pyyaml>=6.0` | YAML config files |
| `httpx>=0.27.0` | HTTP client for API calls |
| `pandas>=2.0` | DataFrame core |
| `pyarrow>=14.0` | Parquet export |
| `openpyxl>=3.1.0` | Excel export |
| `rich>=13.0` | CLI formatting + progress |

